<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.1.4">
<l>tōyam parantanaṭu vucūḻaliltol laivaṭivu koṇṭa</l>
<l>māyakkuḻavi yataṉai nāṭuṟil vammiṉcu vaṭuraikkē</l>
<l>ṉāyar maṭamakaḷpiṉ ṉaikkā kiyaṭalviṭai yēḻiṉaiyum</l>
<l>vīyappo rutuviyart tuniṉṟāṉai meymmaiyē kaṇṭāruḷar.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If [you] seek the wondrous babe who took an ancient form</l>
<l rend="indent">in the midst of the surrounding vast waters,</l>
<l>come! I’ll give you a hint.</l>
<l>There are those who truly saw him standing,</l>
<l rend="indent">angrily fighting the seven battle-bulls so that they died,</l>
<l>for the sake of the simple cowherd woman, Piṉṉai.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
